node.text:
Today, we experimented with food coloring, milk, and dish soap! What do you think happened when we tried to mix it all together? Magic! What color would you use?

#learningthroughplay #liaandmaya

node.text: Lia is obsessed with chocolate so I try to limit her sugar intake as much as I can, so when a friend of mine recommended @elsenutrition I jumped on it. They are a complete plant-based nutritional kids drink and they have a chocolate flavor! The other great thing is that it contains all vitamins kids need. 👊🏻 So we gave it a try and the kids really love it. Maya prefers the vanilla flavor. Here we are making delicious banana and strawberry smoothie drinks. Next up I’m gonna try chocolate ice cream 😋😋 What is your favorite smoothie flavor? Try out @elsenutrition use code LIAMAYA25 at elsenutrition.com for 25% off! #ElsePartner

node.text:
On June 19th you turned 4. 
It was a very emotional weekend for me because time is just flying like crazy and the kids getting older isn’t such an easy transition to me. 
Maya had the best time with all her friends and most importantly Elsa came with Anna, Kristoff, Sven and Olaf! Her eyes literally blew up when she saw all those characters walk in! She was in heaven 🤩 
Happy Birthday to my golden baby! My affectionate, caring, big hearted, and incredibly smart girl! We love you so much!!! 😘😘😘

node.text:
Ok so it’s no secret that my girls are obsessed with Disney princesses… and right now their biggest obsession is Elsa and Ariel 😍 
This is not the first time I’m posting about @nathalies_dolls and probably also not the last! She is one of the most talented people I know. No joke! She hand makes GORGEOUS dolls and not just Disney characters but she can even make a custom doll that looks like you!
She made one of Lia almost 5 years ago and it is still one of my favorite dolls!!!! 
Besides this, she also donates proceeds of her sales to this wonderful cause @friendsofunfpa 🙌🏻🙏🏻 They donate birth kits to moms in need and so much more!!

Please take a moment and take a look at @nathalies_dolls she truly is amazing!! 
These dolls are the Bentley of all dolls! 😍😍 Thank you so much for once again making my girls the most beautiful dolls 🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻
